  "description": "Wavetable at position 0.5 for a chest-heavy mid-table timbral anchor. Breach sub high, hunt macro active at 0.4 — the predator logic adds rhythmic compression and weight to the low end. Echo resonance adds tail without muddying the attack. A bass that has presence and authority in any mix.",
